{"tid":685140,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"做左小學私補6年 心得交流","createTime":"2018-05-31T07:35:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-05T09:33:05.000Z","uid":188928,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"0c795ab0c2d2526345bc3ae6d96dd752c438d6a6","tid":685140,"uid":188928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T07:35:00.000Z","msg":"做左小學私補6年，遇過唔少趣事，有怪獸家長，有好nice 嘅家長。學生就基本上全部都好可愛。<br />\n有咩問題想知我都會盡量分享<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bff07f710db725fa03b158a27e53d3979be2e93b","tid":685140,"uid":161322,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T07:44:07.000Z","msg":"分享吓啲細路補補吓扭計/同老母嗌交點處理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4197cd3cf74f0bbc03f7013dba6d5bf4b6668d8b","tid":685140,"uid":182286,"like":8,"dislike":8,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T07:44:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7cc412310b54acf9d82b8f90dc0da22fbb028aab","tid":685140,"uid":188928,"like":2,"dislike":22,"score":-20,"quote":{"pid":"bff07f710db725fa03b158a27e53d3979be2e93b","tid":685140,"uid":161322,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T07:44:07.000Z","msg":"分享吓啲細路補補吓扭計/同老母嗌交點處理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T09:20:16.000Z","msg":"細路扭計有幾個階段XD 最初我一定會氹下先, 同佢講做完功課/溫完書就可以睇陣電視or食糖咁..<br />\n佢地唔聽我就會開始嬲嬲地, 黑黑地面, 大聲少少, 通常佢地開始驚, 就會唔情願咁做下野<br />\n試過真係搞唔掂我就會扮慘, 同佢地講話你再係咁我就會被你媽媽炒左, 會俾你媽媽鬧咁... 佢地通常都會可憐我XD<br />\n<br />\n咁最後都會請返佢地食糖or送小禮物ge.. 糖同貼紙係每次必備的~<br />\n其實會發現小朋友其實好天真可愛, 送張貼紙俾佢就唔會記得我頭先鬧過佢地了~"},{"pid":"4bd1e33af42f5ebb023e49215dc3e15e76695039","tid":685140,"uid":188928,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"4197cd3cf74f0bbc03f7013dba6d5bf4b6668d8b","tid":685140,"uid":182286,"like":8,"dislike":8,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T07:44:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T09:20:43.000Z","msg":"冇啦~<br />\n利申:真絲"},{"pid":"9407f17d